org.eclipse.papyrus.MARTE.MARTE_DesignModel.HLAM

Interface HLAMPackage.Literals

  • Enclosing interface:
    HLAMPackage

    public static interface HLAMPackage.Literals
    Defines literals for the meta objects that represent
    • each class,
    • each feature of each class,
    • each enum,
    • and each data type
